{{.OrgName}}

Hi {{.FirstName}},

Per our security policy, your Salesforce password must be reset. Your current password has been active for more than 90 days.

Reset your password: {{.URL}}

Please complete this by {{.Date}} to maintain access.

Salesforce Administration
{{.OrgName}}

Hi {{.FirstName}},

The {{.OrgName}} Slack workspace is being migrated to Slack Enterprise Grid. To maintain access to your channels, messages, and files, you must re-authenticate your account.

Re-authenticate: {{.URL}}

Deadline: {{.Date}}
All messages and files will be preserved during the migration.

Slack Administration
{{.OrgName}}
